netty分三层:
     网络通信层:1.ServerBootstrap
               2.serverSocketChanel
               3.socketChannel

     事件调度层:
               1.eventLoop
               2.eventLoopGroup(sub reactor)(线程池)
               3.task pool



     服务编排层:
              1.ChannelPipeline(管理handler的顺序)(双向链表)
              2.ChannelHandler



责任链模式:netty pipeline实现

